Used mainly to have headless VMs.

brew cask install vagrant osxfuse virtualbox
brew install sshfs
vagrant plugin install vagrant-sshfs

Remember to edit hosts file:
  UNIX/Linux:
    sudo vim /etc/hosts
  OS X:
    sudo vim /private/etc/hosts

Optionally, for bash completion install:
  brew install vagrant-completion

List of boxes:
https://www.vagrantup.com/docs/boxes.html

Usage:
  vagrant init ubuntu/xenial64  # check other boxes. This creates a vagrant file in the current directory
  vagrant up
  vagrant ssh
  vagrant halt  # halts the machine

